lyrics: I'm not afraid to take a stand, everyone come take my hand
Hello from the other side, I must have called a thousand times
I been movin' calm, don't start no trouble with me
Shine bright like a diamond, we're beautiful like diamonds in the sky
Cause we got a long list of ex-lovers, they'll tell you I'm insane
Hey Jude, don't make it bad, take a sad song and make it better
Is this the real life? Is this just fantasy? Caught in a landslide
My left stroke just went viral, right stroke put lil' baby in a spiral
So you're a tough guy, like it really rough guy, just can't get enough guy
I'm in love with the shape of you, we push and pull like a magnet do
